The tendency of the subconscious is life ward

  • Over 90% of your mental life is subconscious, so those who fail to make use of this marvellous power live within very narrow limits
  • Your subconscious mind is the builder of your body and is on the job 24 hours a day. You interfere with its life giving patterns by negative thinking
  • Watch your thoughts. Every thought accepted as true is brought into your world as a reality
  • The tendency of your subconscious mind is always lifeward, your job is with your conscious mind. Feed your subconscious mind with premises which are true. Your subconscious is always reproducing according to your habitual mental patterns
